The '''Embassy of Belgium in Washington, D.C.''' is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[Belgium|Kingdom of Belgium]] to the [[United States]]. The [[diplomatic mission#Naming| chancery]] is located at 3330 Garfield Street, [[Northwest, Washington, D.C.]]<ref>http://www.embassy.org/embassies/be.html</ref>
Belgium also operates consulates general in [[Los Angeles]] and [[New York City|New York]], and a consulate in [[Atlanta]]. In addition, several [[Communities, regions and language areas of Belgium|communities and regions]] of Belgium also have diplomatic representations in the United States.
The Belgian ambassador to the United States is [[Dirk Wouters]].<ref>http://www.diplobel.us/Ambassador/ambassador.asp</ref>
