'''''Lekce tvůrčího psaní''''' (''The Creative Writing Lesson'') is a [[Czech language|Czech]] psychological novella, written by [[Michal Viewegh]]. It was first published in 2005. A [[Slovenian language|Slovenian]] edition was published in 2010.<ref name="Dana Blatná" />

