'''''Syndicat professionnel des commerçants et transporteurs africains du Congo''''' was an [[employers' organization]] in [[République du Moyen-Congo|Moyen-Congo]]. It was formed by African employers, as an alternative to the French-dominated [[COLPAEF]]. Ayina was the president of the organization.<ref>Bazenguissa-Ganga, Rémy. ''[https://books.google.com/books?id=15Qza8LQcFMC Les voies du politique au Congo: essai de sociologie historique]''. Paris: Karthala, 1997. p. 36</ref>

